    "name": "Gridlink",
    "steam_appid": 3176800,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gridlink is a fun, minimalist puzzle game. While the rules of the game are simple and easy to understand, the game offers enough complexity to keep you entertained for a few minutes or a few hours.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The aim of the game is to draw a continuous line starting from the smallest number on the grid, to the next number in an ascending order and ending the line on the largest number on the grid. Each part of the line can be drawn separately, as long as it still respects the rules and at the end everything connects up to a single line.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176800/extras/20df1f9117d2e980fa5d0011df5a7cd2.avif?t=1726777824\" width=418 height=418 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The puzzle is solved when all the numbers are connected, each cell in the grid has been passed and the line does not cross itself.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176800/extras/88eab67ae0ad49de861674b8a21555c4.avif?t=1726777824\" width=420 height=416 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you make a mistake at any point in the game, you always have the option of <strong>unlimited UNDOs</strong> or clearing the board entirely.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176800/extras/770d26d3436db69d608dee3ec66a39c3.avif?t=1726777824\" width=242 height=122 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The pre-generated levels not to your liking? No problem! Use the custom level generator and setup the game grid with the size and difficulty of your choosing.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176800/extras/7bd2e112fd8f9b2f8fd720a11704cd50.avif?t=1726777824\" width=598 height=304 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>FEATURES</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 150 pre-generated levels ranging from easy (6x6 grid) to difficult (20x20 grid)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > A custom level generator allowing you to choose any difficulty you want</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Minimalist design</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Relaxing background music</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Unlimited UNDO options if you make a mistake</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dark Mode</p></li></ul>",
